ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='sparql_query', args='{""query"": ""PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?prop ?label ?alc ?mpc WHERE {\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n  {\\n    ?zone s223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  } UNION {\\n    ?zone s223:encloses ?space .\\n    ?space s223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  } UNION {\\n    ?zone s223:hasConnectionPoint ?cp .\\n    ?cp s223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  }\\n  ?prop a ?ptype .\\n  FILTER(?ptype IN (s223:QuantifiableObservableProperty, s223:EnumeratedObservableProperty, s223:QuantifiableActuatableProperty, s223:EnumeratedActuatableProperty))\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop rdfs:label ?label . }\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?prop s223:hasExternalReference ?ext .\\n    ?ext brick:endpoint ?endpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?ext brick:source ?src . }\\n    BIND(IF(CONTAINS(LCASE(str(?src)), \\""alc\\""), str(?endpoint), \\""\\"") AS ?alc)\\n    BIND(IF(CONTAINS(LCASE(str(?src)), \\""mpc\\""), str(?endpoint), \\""\\"") AS ?mpc)\\n  }\\n  ?prop brick:writable ?writable .\\n  FILTER(?writable = false)\\n}\\nLIMIT 100"", ""result_length"": 100}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-55729c49bcba4cf2818e8da3999caf7a', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 5, 54, 35, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[ToolCallPart(tool_name='sparql_query', args='{""query"":""PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?prop ?label (SAMPLE(?alc_ep) AS ?alc_endpoint) (SAMPLE(?mpc_ep) AS ?mpc_endpoint)\\nWHERE {\\n  # Zones and associated properties\\n  ?zone a s223:Zone .\\n  { ?zone s223:hasProperty ?prop . }\\n  UNION {\\n    ?zone s223:encloses ?space .\\n    ?space s223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  }\\n  UNION {\\n    ?zone s223:hasConnectionPoint ?cp .\\n    ?cp s223:hasProperty ?prop .\\n  }\\n  # Property labeling\\n  OPTIONAL { ?prop rdfs:label ?label . }\\n  # Read-only flag\\n  ?prop brick:writable ?writable .\\n  FILTER(?writable = false)\\n  # External references\\n  OPTIONAL {\\n    ?prop s223:hasExternalReference ?ext .\\n    ?ext brick:endpoint ?endpoint .\\n    OPTIONAL { ?ext brick:source ?src . }\\n    BIND(IF(CONTAINS(LCASE(str(?src)), \\""alc\\"", ?endpoint) AS ?alc_ep)\\n    BIND(IF(CONTAINS(LCASE(str(?src)), \\""mpc\\"", ?endpoint) AS ?mpc_ep)\\n  }\\n}\\nGROUP BY ?prop ?label\\nLIMIT 200""], ""result_length"": 200}', tool_call_id='chatcmpl-tool-be35fc1fad95435fa96fba973f59b07c', part_kind='tool-call')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 5, 54, 39, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')","PREFIX s223: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ashrae: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX qudt: <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?heatPump ?property ?value ?unit ?endpoint\\nWHERE {\\n  # Identify the UFT zone (reheat) that contains the heat pump\\n  ?uft a ashrae:UFT .\\n  ?uft ashrae:contains ?heatPump .\\n\\n  # The heat pump must be a watertowater heat pump\\n  ?heatPump a ashrae:WatertoWaterHeatPump .\\n\\n  # The heat pump has a property that is an observable (nonwritable) quantity\\n  ?heatPump ashrae:hasProperty ?property .\\n  ?property a ashrae:QuantifiableObservableProperty .\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?property brick:writable true }\\n\\n  # The property observes a measurement/value\\n  ?property ashrae:observes ?observation .\\n  ?observation ashrae:hasValue ?value .\\n  OPTIONAL { ?observation qudt:hasUnit ?unit . }\\n\\n  # Reference endpoints for the observation (if any)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?observation brick:endpoint ?endpoint . }\\n}\\nLIMIT 100""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 6, 14, 56, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ashrae: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX qudt: <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?heatPump ?property ?value ?unit ?endpoint\\nWHERE {\\n  # Identify the UFT zone (reheat) that contains the heat pump\\n  ?uft a ashrae:UFT .\\n  ?uft ashrae:contains ?heatPump .\\n\\n  # The heat pump must be a watertowater heat pump\\n  ?heatPump a ashrae:WatertoWaterHeatPump .\\n\\n  # The heat pump has a property that is an observable (nonwritable) quantity\\n  ?heatPump ashrae:hasProperty ?property .\\n  ?property a ashrae:QuantifiableObservableProperty .\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?property brick:writable true }\\n\\n  # The property observes a measurement/value\\n  ?property ashrae:observes ?observation .\\n  ?observation ashrae:hasValue ?value .\\n  OPTIONAL { ?observation qudt:hasUnit ?unit . }\\n\\n  # Reference endpoints for the observation (if any)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?observation brick:endpoint ?endpoint . }\\n}\\nLIMIT 100""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 6, 14, 56, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')

ModelResponse(parts=[TextPart(content='{\n  ""sparql_query"": ""PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>\\nPREFIX brick: <https://brickschema.org/schema/Brick/>\\nPREFIX ashrae: <http://data.ashrae.org/standard223#>\\nPREFIX qudt: <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/>\\n\\nSELECT DISTINCT ?heatPump ?property ?value ?unit ?endpoint\\nWHERE {\\n  # Identify the UFT zone (reheat) that contains the heat pump\\n  ?uft a ashrae:UFT .\\n  ?uft ashrae:contains ?heatPump .\\n\\n  # The heat pump must be a watertowater heat pump\\n  ?heatPump a ashrae:WatertoWaterHeatPump .\\n\\n  # The heat pump has a property that is an observable (nonwritable) quantity\\n  ?heatPump ashrae:hasProperty ?property .\\n  ?property a ashrae:QuantifiableObservableProperty .\\n  FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?property brick:writable true }\\n\\n  # The property observes a measurement/value\\n  ?property ashrae:observes ?observation .\\n  ?observation ashrae:hasValue ?value .\\n  OPTIONAL { ?observation qudt:hasUnit ?unit . }\\n\\n  # Reference endpoints for the observation (if any)\\n  OPTIONAL { ?observation brick:endpoint ?endpoint . }\\n}\\nLIMIT 100""\n}', part_kind='text')], model_name='hosted_vllm/hosted_vllm/gpt-oss-120b', timestamp=datetime.datetime(2026, 1, 22, 6, 14, 56, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), kind='response')
